org.eclipse.scada.configuration.modbus

Interface ModbusDevice

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Device, Documentable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ModbusDeviceImpl

    public interface ModbusDevice
extends Device
    A representation of the model object 'Device'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Port
    • Protocol Type
    • Inter Frame Delay
    • Slaves
    • Type System

    See Also:
    ModbusPackage.getModbusDevice()
